cat << EOF
adesklets is an interactive Imlib2  console for the X Window system.
It provides scripted languages with a clean and simple way to write great
looking, mildly interactive desktop integrated graphic applets (aka desklets).
It can also be used as a command line oriented graphic editor, a bit
similar to ImageMagick , but with different functionality.
EOF
